We model epidemic spreading in the period from 21 February 2020 to 2 May 2020 using reported data by MoHME.2 The Runge–Kutta method is used to solve the ordinary differential equations in MATLAB. As shown in Figure 1, we estimated the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
